{"tid":84832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無聊一問，點解龍會係Dragon","createTime":"2017-01-17T23:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T06:02:45.000Z","uid":71110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8750ff2608a48e5412e1612df3a86df65444d0","tid":84832,"uid":71110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:42:30.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西方既龍通常有對翼，識噴火，有利爪同埋住係深山/地獄<br />\n<br />\n東方(起碼中國同日本)既龍基本上係一條識飛既蛇，加兩條觸鬚兩隻角咁，會住天上面又會住海底<br />\n<br />\n明明係兩種生物<br />\n究竟當初係邊個翻譯到佢地一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e784c083ad24d10c6996c9b4214709ca92cb4feb","tid":84832,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:44:24.000Z","msg":"因為自己條龍要&quot;揸緊&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309e335f4401578a53680dda024fc2b89ca73fd8","tid":84832,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為自己條龍要&quot;揸緊&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打改名啦"},{"pid":"4af26389d9c74f1f6d2a69afb34e5f0688f757ad","tid":84832,"uid":37078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:45:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為自己條龍要&quot;揸緊&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打改名啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bccaddef30edfff899a9aba854ef4e86380fff","tid":84832,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T23:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為自己條龍要&quot;揸緊&quot;<img src=\"/asse