9.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實中國都有西方龍<br />\n不過叫應龍咁解</blockquote><br />\n應龍真係未聽過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真e家d人講起龍，好似pad咁都自動波變哂西方龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中國有三種龍<br />\n應龍 蛟龍 虯龍<br />\n蛟龍同虯龍比較似<br />\n蛟龍據天 虯龍據海<br />\n而應龍就應該就係西方龍<br />\n可能東西方兩邊嘅畫有啲唔同<br />\n但特徵都似</blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆我覺得差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都多謝e位巴打既資料"},{"pid":"cd31d0500bc61adf2c7d98ca7dc27608e25648aa","tid":84832,"uid":50678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:07:51.000Z","msg":"Phoenix 都唔係鳳"},{"pid":"93cb10f4fda53f2e575d320490181ad41e90baba","tid":84832,"uid":71110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Phoenix 都唔係鳳</blockquote><br />\n我覺得起碼個樣似d 龍係差好多"},{"pid":"b30c58e0b3b09476d3c7526a2edf07dddd6090ce","tid":84832,"uid":15063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:11:27.000Z","msg":"因為G dragon"},{"pid":"399a8510f2fc5587aa9ab281061201a7f06c6ba5","tid":84832,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:13:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實中國都有西方龍<br />\n不過叫應龍咁解</blockquote><br />\n應龍真係未聽過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真e家d人講起龍，好似pad咁都自動波變哂西方龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中國有三種龍<br />\n應龍 蛟龍 虯龍<br />\n蛟龍同虯龍比較似<br />\n蛟龍據天 虯龍據海<br />\n而應龍就應該就係西方龍<br />\n可能東西方兩邊嘅畫有啲唔同<br />\n但特徵都似</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係咪漏咗一種 Wiki話有四種<br />\n有鱗曰蛟龍,有翼曰應龍,有角曰虯龍,無角曰螭龍"},{"pid":"d48d9c3a09ec0de6a024746d60d040b7152767f0","tid":84832,"uid":4518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n應龍真係未